{"tid":944283,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果話南宋係嗰個年代既文明最佳守護者應該無人會反對","createTime":"2018-12-17T04:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T06:56:50.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e4b16b1e4f73ec42a0b2327d28d6e7ebd6f6ee","tid":944283,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:49:46.000Z","msg":"淨係襄陽一役拖左蒙古四十幾年已經救左佢地南面好多民族<br />\n<br />\n調返轉睇如果南宋一早亡左<br />\n果四十幾年時間蒙古仲係處於極高士氣既擴張階段<br />\n<br />\n南面領土面積隨時伸延晒成個東南亞 問題係會唔會夠時間踩到過澳洲果邊，造成更大文明浩劫 當然果啲地方喺當時黎講談唔上有咩文化文明，但一定會大開殺戒搞到血流成河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之南宋真係一啲都唔廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bbba1f02937dbc769c09a9ee811b2fbe26d172","tid":944283,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"越南都打贏過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0315e5d8e71210459bdc5c4050aaeb7bee41836d","tid":944283,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e2bbba1f02937dbc769c09a9ee811b2fbe26d172","tid":944283,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"越南都打贏過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:57:24.000Z","msg":"越南會唔會太近中國<br />\n依家係想像下如果一早中門大開<br />\n成個地區實會好大件事 因為蒙古係癲架，歐洲果啲以佢地果陣水平都唔撚知邊度既地方都要去西征去殺人搶地 如果南宋早就捱唔住 你可唔可以保證蒙古唔會咬埋落宋以南大量土地<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔係南宋既功勞 真係唔知讚邊個 讚阿里不哥同忽必烈內鬥？<br />\n你"},{"pid":"02a90584c140486f2e1cbad2a3f25b26961eb289","tid":944283,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0315e5d8e71210459bdc5c4050aaeb7bee41836d","tid":944283,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e2bbba1f02937dbc769c09a9ee811b2fbe26d172","tid":944283,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:53:14.000Z","msg"